title: BioFrontiers Interdisciplinary Quantitative (IQ) Biology PhD Program Fund
description: This fund offers fellowships to provide the science and engineering leaders of the future with biological, computational, and mathematical knowledge to fully assess and solve modern scientific problems in human health and welfare.
